   1 REM Countdown v1
   5 BORDER 0: PAPER 0: INK 7: CLS
  10 REM === Red fill with rising tone ===
  12 FOR i=0 TO 21
  14 FOR j=0 TO 31
  16 PRINT AT i,j; PAPER 2;" "
